Resource Profile: Process

Official URL: https://profiles.ihe.net/ITI/mCSD/StructureDefinition/IHE.mCSD.ProcessCareServices Version: 4.0.0
Active as of 2025-05-21 Computable Name: MCSDProcessCareServices

A profile on the Bundle transaction for ITI-130 Process Care Services Resources Request Message

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Bundle/Example-MCSD
